      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "详细解释这里在干什么；\n这里的500是什么单位什么意思，后面定时器100hz又是什么意思，就是说\n0.01s调依次puppy函数嘛？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "详细解释这里在干什么；\n这里的500是什么单位什么意思，后面定时器100hz又是什么意思，就是说0.01s调依次puppy函数嘛？",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Kjt7ElxLyJoubbj_pdgVk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 587.559044510788,
      "y": 1811.3698760932534,
      "width": 682.919921875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1367820574,
      "version": 188,
      "versionNonce": 259846919,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这段代码是在做“上电初始化”：四足先进入默认停止姿态，机械臂 10/11 走到\n默认位，9 号舵机回中，然后启动一个 100Hz 的 ROS 发布循环。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这段代码是在做“上电初始化”：四足先进入默认停止姿态，机械臂 10/11 走到默认位，9 号舵机回中，然后启动一个 100Hz 的 ROS 发布循环。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
