      "versionNonce": 779335559,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "把机械臂末端移动到目标坐标；坐标单位是 cm，500 明确就是 ms",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "把机械臂末端移动到目标坐标；坐标单位是 cm，500 明确就是 ms",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
