      "seed": 2031656130,
      "version": 61,
      "versionNonce": 1916874407,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "单独把 9 号舵机打到 1500 脉宽，耗时 300ms；结合带机械臂示例看，\n9/10/11 是机械臂三路舵机，所以这一步是在补机械臂第 3 路的初始位",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "单独把 9 号舵机打到 1500 脉宽，耗时 300ms；结合带机械臂示例看，9/10/11 是机械臂三路舵机，所以这一步是在补机械臂第 3 路的初始位",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8mWzoxSqksls4giodSIUw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 590.8014806095931,
      "y": 1770.242437630957,
      "width": 550.2599487304688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
