      "seed": 965432817,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1998518665,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "它的作用是：把标准 ROS 速度命令翻译成 Puppy 内部速度命令",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "它的作用是：把标准 ROS 速度命令翻译成 Puppy 内部速度命令",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-z0igT1tKrp56hqdcU15P",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3627.7317145928205,
      "y": 4313.46964879255,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3C",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2012347807,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1234042759,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "处理逻辑分两种：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "处理逻辑分两种：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TLDbtiDkpyKGwnL1wyi-V",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3482.781870232469,
      "y": 4348.46964879255,
      "width": 449.8996887207031,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 913141713,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1576591465,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果 abs(linear.x) > 0.5 或 abs(angular.z) > 0.5",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果 abs(linear.x) > 0.5 或 abs(angular.z) > 0.5",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IF8rKDHXhJX-0_bOdzjmi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3614.91173778618,
      "y": 4383.46964879255,
      "width": 185.63995361328125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3E",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1161753023,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1121089191,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "先把姿态切到 Stand",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "先把姿态切到 Stand",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yScp_a4tesfrdhuuGZ25z",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3587.7317145928205,
      "y": 4418.46964879255,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3F",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1739673009,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1655892809,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "然后比较平移和转向谁更大",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "然后比较平移和转向谁更大",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ADqwzO8L-egCjuSP4cqNZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3500.5717567070783,
      "y": 4453.46964879255,
      "width": 414.3199157714844,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 555246047,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 112921031,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果平移主导，就发一个前进/后退的 Velocity",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果平移主导，就发一个前进/后退的 Velocity",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "fjoqoT_SsPV0j6YgQfRiJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3506.181742058641,
      "y": 4488.46964879255,
      "width": 403.0999450683594,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1686007697,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 497588777,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果转向主导，就发一个原地转向的 Velocity",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果转向主导，就发一个原地转向的 Velocity",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mva0pZPmk0u1ybs_aZRO4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3647.7317145928205,
      "y": 4523.46964879255,
      "width": 120,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2089733631,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1650735335,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "具体映射是：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "具体映射是：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CTRj575RLOBvrdX_3lRmH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3620.311754570848,
      "y": 4558.46964879255,
      "width": 174.8399200439453,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1930188145,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 264596745,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "linear.x 被压成 ±16",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "linear.x 被压成 ±16",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q-PFxzmqU_j702NqXxwTi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3539.8517707451642,
      "y": 4593.46964879255,
      "width": 335.7598876953125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1386395167,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1264223239,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "angular.z 被压成 ±25°/s 对应的弧度",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "angular.z 被压成 ±25°/s 对应的弧度",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xa-zga-vW_D44kNQHD0kG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3539.161783562547,
      "y": 4628.46964879255,
      "width": 337.1398620605469,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 648183633,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 277144553,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果 linear.x == 0 且 angular.z == 0",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果 linear.x == 0 且 angular.z == 0",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BrcAZW4sAw_hBfFfQI2dD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3553.141779290086,
      "y": 4663.46964879255,
      "width": 309.17987060546875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1782880831,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1369074471,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "就调用 VelocityFun(0,0,0) 停下来",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "就调用 VelocityFun(0,0,0) 停下来",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nHv083QAEJr5x4Q4t9c6a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3647.7317145928205,
      "y": 4698.46964879255,
      "width": 120,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1033399601,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 2079489737,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "它有个特点：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "它有个特点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GrlldpSGGuU1zFIxygxtd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3617.7317145928205,
      "y": 4733.46964879255,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1481964127,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1368419911,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "只响应比较大的输入",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "只响应比较大的输入",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zVSm4S41SPMNBZah_P8sY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3513.091715203172,
      "y": 4768.46964879255,
      "width": 389.2799987792969,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1062575889,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 547995049,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "小于阈值但又不等于 0 的输入，会被忽略掉",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "小于阈值但又不等于 0 的输入，会被忽略掉",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9swvW-nbIX5DRgG7H6EEJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3453.7217353447736,
      "y": 4803.46964879255,
      "width": 508.01995849609375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1101289087,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 1712917863,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "所以它更像“遥控/导航兼容入口”，不是高精度速度通道。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "所以它更像“遥控/导航兼容入口”，不是高精度速度通道。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vGcr9IkuiRwdG-Wnibwym",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3497.814030899697,
      "y": 4858.82471722234,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3R",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 45305009,
      "version": 39,
      "versionNonce": 1842749577,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364211,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这个速度最后给谁用了",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
