      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为什么这四个参数就可以改变步态？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为什么这四个参数就可以改变步态？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "d3NTqPzunZD9YEdb4iD9i",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1887.349033123778,
      "y": 4368.9474820260775,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 614345392,
      "version": 71,
      "versionNonce": 229939721,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为什么要存一个全局变量，哪一步需要用？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为什么要存一个全局变量，哪一步需要用？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yuJ49lN9s4-JMnnwVxQV7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2248.2298399191595,
      "y": 304.7739648256906,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 121381456,
      "version": 115,
      "versionNonce": 1224779527,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "需要看一下底层步态使用的是什么摆动方法；例如摆钟线",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "需要看一下底层步态使用的是什么摆动方法；例如摆钟线",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "G3as655lc2eOqTUUxAQll",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1920.6954499994547,
      "y": 4399.919526649459,
      "width": 631.619873046875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 758725712,
      "version": 164,
      "versionNonce": 1107718377,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "往下层传递主要是 gait_config, 全局变量只是缓存使用，方便上层回调\n之间复用",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "往下层传递主要是 gait_config, 全局变量只是缓存使用，方便上层回调\n之间复用",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zvwSH4ICky78yEvSb7L-a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1907.7787324701578,
      "y": 4522.002847267135,
      "width": 680.5999755859375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6R",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 990975056,
      "version": 33,
      "versionNonce": 478424615,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "因为这个项目里“步态”被定义得比较窄：它主要就是“落脚时序 + 抬脚轨迹”，\n不是整个运动控制",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "因为这个项目里“步态”被定义得比较窄：它主要就是“落脚时序 + 抬脚轨迹”，\n不是整个运动控制",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zvbDmHJawb63ObYDR9nOL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1911.9010567896416,
      "y": 4659.221401261763,
      "width": 565.9998779296875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6S",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 484572848,
      "version": 93,
      "versionNonce": 2142923721,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "整个运动被拆成三层：姿态由 stance_config(...) 管，速度方向\n由 move(...) 管，步态节奏由 gait_config(...) 管",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "整个运动被拆成三层：姿态由 stance_config(...) 管，速度方向由 move(...) 管，步态节奏由 gait_config(...) 管",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "phdHNavf19zeULYY-nwuD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1913.5357918970633,
      "y": 4728.918389454235,
      "width": 579.7000122070312,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6T",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1606591056,
      "version": 73,
      "versionNonce": 1078579527,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4 个量分别控制：多脚重叠支撑时间、摆腿离地时间、前后脚相位\n间隔、抬脚高度",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4 个量分别控制：多脚重叠支撑时间、摆腿离地时间、前后脚相位间隔、抬脚高度",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PmIvh0d1pMej7k9JMFL95",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1901.563084319955,
      "y": 4796.280480590182,
      "width": 576.7999877929688,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6U",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 242754736,
      "version": 87,
      "versionNonce": 518785705,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "一旦你改变“谁先落地、重叠多久、离地多久、脚抬多高”，机器狗\n看起来就已经是在换步态了。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "一旦你改变“谁先落地、重叠多久、离地多久、脚抬多高”，机器狗看起来就已经是在换步态了。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QH8kp4Lkbi5kgHncTxNcm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900.763079447891,
      "y": 4905.877416370324,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6V",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 756492976,
      "version": 86,
      "versionNonce": 497946727,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "***这 4 个参数只够描述“这个库支持的那一类步态”，不代表能描述\n所有四足机器人步态。更复杂的控制还会需要每条腿独立相位、足端\n轨迹曲线、地面反馈等",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "***这 4 个参数只够描述“这个库支持的那一类步态”，不代表能描述\n所有四足机器人步态。更复杂的控制还会需要每条腿独立相位、足端\n轨迹曲线、地面反馈等",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "z1qMx-7YkA7Xnf2rnmDwZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1934.889103918639,
      "y": 4572.345183387238,
      "width": 651,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6X",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 56346800,
      "version": 169,
      "versionNonce": 1749470601,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这里的整个运动控制？它是由什么组成，为什么说落腿时序+抬腿轨迹不能\n完全表示？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这里的整个运动控制？它是由什么组成，为什么说落腿时序+抬腿轨迹不能\n完全表示？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
