      "text": "velocity/gait/pose",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "ag2F7jzHFI5PrwjevqXg5",
      "originalText": "velocity/gait/pose",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JCOVmjNWZqJirssh4OtC6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 694.1713364855972,
      "y": 7579.237396242694,
      "width": 1247.595947265625,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6n",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 759852220,
      "version": 204,
      "versionNonce": 707482313,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "走的是导航，上位机发送信号 /goal_pose；然后后端control server，把 pose 变为轨迹和连续速度",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "走的是导航，上位机发送信号 /goal_pose；然后后端control server，把 pose 变为轨迹和连续速度",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "B8_uq7NrN3wwDidqN4Y1p",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 705.2824475967083,
      "y": 7669.237396242694,
      "width": 1074.583984375,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6o",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1115724988,
      "version": 140,
      "versionNonce": 1593760327,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "激光雷达避障，给“线速度/角速度”任务，这里发送的就是 /cmd_vel 和 /cmd_vel_nav",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "激光雷达避障，给“线速度/角速度”任务，这里发送的就是 /cmd_vel 和 /cmd_vel_nav",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hD1_GdPnRHpGtNhC-1DeX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 711.2824747234444,
      "y": 7775.459591338181,
      "width": 1255.2958984375,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6p",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1258322692,
      "version": 365,
      "versionNonce": 950538665,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774929364212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "比如说巡线，手柄，小跑，这种自己走，但是受控制并不走上层规划，而是直接调用 gait，pose，vel",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "比如说巡线，手柄，小跑，这种自己走，但是受控制并不走上层规划，而是直接调用 gait，pose，vel",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
