      "version": 345,
      "versionNonce": 1117586697,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "0OQJHBvoIGlJkibyS7nFW",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1774940506762,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. deactivated\nactivate = true, 先发一个激活状态，将状态 从\nde 切换到 rest\n2. mode == reset  v =0 ， yaw_rate = 0\n\n3. mode = trot and state ！= trot\ntrot_event = true，发送state 状态切换到trot\n4. mode = rest and state = trot",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. deactivated\nactivate = true, 先发一个激活状态，将状态 从\nde 切换到 rest\n2. mode == reset  v =0 ， yaw_rate = 0\n\n3. mode = trot and state ！= trot\ntrot_event = true，发送state 状态切换到trot\n4. mode = rest and state = trot",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
