      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "activate_event        DEACTIVATED -> REST，REST -> DEACTIVATED，映射\n见 Controller.py (line 42)        切完后如果是 REST，走 Controller.py (line 150) 的\n静站/姿态控制分支；如果切到 DEACTIVATED，这个 run() 里没有专门分支，通常由外\n层流程停掉",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "activate_event        DEACTIVATED -> REST，REST -> DEACTIVATED，映射见 Controller.py (line 42)        切完后如果是 REST，走 Controller.py (line 150) 的静站/姿态控制分支；如果切到 DEACTIVATED，这个 run() 里没有专门分支，通常由外层流程停掉",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qxnuDLzqiPHMjp0xR0PDH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -442.89999580257825,
      "y": 2645.0358277487885,
      "width": 772.259521484375,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9Z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 527893161,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1823194247,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774940910142,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "trot_event        REST -> TROT，TROT -> REST，HOP -> TROT，\nFINISHHOP -> TROT，映射见 Controller.py (line 41)        切到 TROT 后走\nController.py (line 99) 的 gait 分支：step_gait() -> stance/swing 脚端更新 -> IK",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "trot_event        REST -> TROT，TROT -> REST，HOP -> TROT，FINISHHOP -> TROT，映射见 Controller.py (line 41)        切到 TROT 后走 Controller.py (line 99) 的 gait 分支：step_gait() -> stance/swing 脚端更新 -> IK",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7Yf5dWWNgO6IxzPagVchS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -438.16123644385425,
