      "text": "hop_event        REST -> HOP，HOP -> FINISHHOP，FINISHHOP -> REST，\nTROT -> HOP，映射见 Controller.py (line 40)        切到 HOP 后走 Controller.py\n(line 130)；切到 FINISHHOP 后走 Controller.py (line 140)；切回 REST 后走\nController.py (line 150)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "hop_event        REST -> HOP，HOP -> FINISHHOP，FINISHHOP -> REST，TROT -> HOP，映射见 Controller.py (line 40)        切到 HOP 后走 Controller.py (line 130)；切到 FINISHHOP 后走 Controller.py (line 140)；切回 REST 后走 Controller.py (line 150)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
