      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "vx误差 -> 修正 command.vx",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "vx误差 -> 修正 command.vx",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Y05KYZKuElI3oUdiBobBN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -31.115412754170052,
      "y": 3413.8318945960177,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 567139847,
      "version": 106,
      "versionNonce": 388106345,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774942050247,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为什么需要该反馈修正？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为什么需要该反馈修正？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OrpiJorx0vuhtfnAnn-Oi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -46.081288092742966,
      "y": 3742.3286671961587,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 110550023,
      "version": 373,
      "versionNonce": 628803751,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774942276791,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为什么速度采取的是误差反馈，而姿态采取的是测量值，\n如果是偏转状态，body 本身就需要偏转，再加上姿态\n反馈，不就变慢了吗？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为什么速度采取的是误差反馈，而姿态采取的是测量值，\n如果是偏转状态，body 本身就需要偏转，再加上姿态\n反馈，不就变慢了吗？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "eFkOYmJE2_E3PYlI2Am_l",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -35.30795028811633,
      "y": 3456.0143935247697,
      "width": 503.7598876953125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2095375463,
      "version": 138,
      "versionNonce": 1027042247,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774942163557,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "因为这里的原始 command 只是“期望值”，不是“实际一定\n能做到的结果”。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "因为这里的原始 command 只是“期望值”，不是“实际一定\n能做到的结果”。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xUBcMzznTaYAGKQ0ARhlu",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -25.32837305097064,
      "y": 3521.397439846638,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1959504519,
      "version": 104,
      "versionNonce": 602738215,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774942253984,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这个项目的步态主干本来就主要按命令做规划，\n不会自动保证实际速度和姿态一定跟上。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这个项目的步态主干本来就主要按命令做规划，\n不会自动保证实际速度和姿态一定跟上。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZUt8nxJ_aD3IeE51xHGb5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -30.038296789954018,
      "y": 3587.8350345617705,
      "width": 498.3599853515625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 807881,
      "version": 64,
      "versionNonce": 1007884551,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774942254869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "浮动基座 trot 是动态过程，实际状态一定会偏离命令。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "浮动基座 trot 是动态过程，实际状态一定会偏离命令。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Zh05XByB8DQ9vOLrQtyRk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -35.65915142623487,
      "y": 3633.181299355642,
      "width": 416.79998779296875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1539162727,
      "version": 80,
      "versionNonce": 696221353,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774942264890,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这层反馈是在补“命令和真实状态之间的误差”。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这层反馈是在补“命令和真实状态之间的误差”。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6-Fe-wRC78mcSmiZzV19R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -34.918704991022764,
      "y": 3675.363999426607,
      "width": 558.7399291992188,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1162720073,
      "version": 48,
      "versionNonce": 1556227239,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774942274794,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "它放在 command 层，是因为这是对现有代码侵入最小的补法。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "它放在 command 层，是因为这是对现有代码侵入最小的补法。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
