      "text": "* (state.height - z),",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "* (state.height - z),",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cvqrTa-YL_dU1Mz2EHQ1_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5821.972798883416,
      "y": 2898.5340038262516,
      "width": 560.5999145507812,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "TZI_fH3A8Z6HnrvfEmiWD",
        "K1PjIvEkcy6hWAZkVP3us"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1156790505,
      "version": 198,
      "versionNonce": 1763404999,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774944624357,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "我还是不理解这个公式，state.height 是期望值吗？z是测量值",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "我还是不理解这个公式，state.height 是期望值吗？z是测量值",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6DTava6FzYhcQZUq7TMjQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5827.9128318424,
      "y": 2945.034095378986,
      "width": 753.519775390625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "K1PjIvEkcy6hWAZkVP3us"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 244661097,
      "version": 108,
      "versionNonce": 12598247,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774944624357,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "state.height 是目标值/参考值，不是测量值。它在 Controller.py (line 185) 每拍末\n尾由 command.height 写回，所以更准确地说，它是控制器保存的“目标站高状态”。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "state.height 是目标值/参考值，不是测量值。它在 Controller.py (line 185) 每拍末尾由 command.height 写回，所以更准确地说，它是控制器保存的“目标站高状态”。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "685zlF7rlJOt11HE40Nyf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5829.122853815056,
      "y": 3007.4341197930485,
      "width": 719.0997314453125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "K1PjIvEkcy6hWAZkVP3us"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1462299303,
      "version": 128,
      "versionNonce": 1698572039,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774944624357,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这里的 z 不是严格的传感器测量值。它取自 StanceController.py (line 34) 的\nstate.foot_locations[2, leg_index]，也就是“当前这条腿在状态里的脚端 z”。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这里的 z 不是严格的传感器测量值。它取自 StanceController.py (line 34) 的 state.foot_locations[2, leg_index]，也就是“当前这条腿在状态里的脚端 z”。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
