      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774945586388,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "所以这一整段不是在算“当前脚怎么走”，而是在算：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "所以这一整段不是在算“当前脚怎么走”，而是在算：",
