      "versionNonce": 1943875337,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774945969439,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "剩下多少 swing 时间，就按“剩余距离 / 剩余时间”算一个速度，\n让脚刚好在摆动结束时走到 touchdown 点。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "剩下多少 swing 时间，就按“剩余距离 / 剩余时间”算一个速度，\n让脚刚好在摆动结束时走到 touchdown 点。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
